Disclaimer: I am not a designer, but for the time being the following workaround might be viable:

```css
.btn-social.btn-facebook {
    background-color: #4267B2;
}
.btn-social.btn-facebook > :first-child {
    color: #4267B2;
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: 1px;
    text-align: right;
    margin: 4px;
    border-right: none;
    width: 24px;
    padding-right: 2px;
    padding-top: 3px;
    line-height: normal;
}
```
